{"tid":1489803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社工撿催淚彈殼交還警方 被指違法","createTime":"2019-08-20T03:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:56:30.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"710e7a1cef20f8782848261cfc80ab6154c60a22","tid":1489803,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"反修訂《逃犯條例》風波自6月持續至今，警方使用超過1900枚催淚彈，經常在現場遺下不少彈殼。<br />\n<br />\n香港社會工作者總工會會長倫智偉表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">近日將一枚在8月5日施放的催淚彈殼交還警方，卻遭警員指是違法及不恰當</span>。他批評警方說法荒謬，認為警方在施放催淚彈翌日，就應該主動到場撿走彈殼。<br />\n<br />\n法政匯思召集人、大律師吳宗鑾指出，撿起彈殼有構成《火器及彈藥條例》中無牌藏有槍械或彈藥的風險，<span style=\"color: red;\">但認為事主隨後交還警方，反映他沒有意圖收藏相關物品。</span><br />\n<br />\n他又強調，市民自行處理彈殼有一定法律風險，認為警方有責任解釋清楚市民適當處理彈殼的方法，以免市民誤墮法網。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2225153%2F&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=4343a4e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225153/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ba55b8895f00b987977672b615a2a5d1caef4e","tid":1489803,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b242e4636d4053cce34ff30a74315278447794cd","tid":1489803,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":39,"score":-28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近日將一枚在8月5日施放的催淚彈殼交還警方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n社工真係最多Q餘既生物"},{"pid":"c4c01e82256e55c7d20567612c88fe8800dbda0e","tid":1489803,"uid":138760,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"quote":